First, you must compile the BuDDy library.

1) cd buddy-2.4
2) ./configure
3) make
4) make install

To compile the test_case.cpp:

1) g++ -I/usr/local/include test_case.cpp -o test_case -L/usr/local/lib -lbdd

To run the test_case:

1) ./test_case > graph.dot

To generate the graph with GraphViz:

1) dot -Tpng graph.dot -o graph.png

